<div class="modal" id="audio-asset-modal">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title">Add Audio</h4>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>You can add background music or sound effects for the different elements of the GUI. For example, when the player presses a button, or a typing sound when displaying text on the message box.</p>
        <fieldset>
          <legend>Audio file (.ogg, .wav, .mp3):</legend>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
              <div class="custom-file">
                <input type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="audio-input">
                <label class="custom-file-label" for="audio-input">Choose file</label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <audio controls class="audio-preview collapse" src="">
            Your browser does not support the
            <code>audio</code> element.
          </audio>
          <legend>Audio Name</legend>
          <small class="form-text text-muted">The name will be used as key to refer to this asset inside the game. Make sure it's unique across all the assets.</small>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input class="form-control reset-input" id="audio-name" oninput="checkUniqueName(this,'audio')">
          </div>
          <legend>Audio Type</legend>
          <div class="form-check">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="audioType" id="audioTypeMusic" value="music">
            <label class="form-check-label" for="audioTypeMusic">
              Music
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-check">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="audioType" id="audioTypeSFX" value="sfx" checked>
            <label class="form-check-label" for="audioTypeSFX">
              Sound Effect
            </label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary upload-asset" onclick="uploadAudio()" data-dismiss="modal">Add</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal" id="font-asset-modal">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title">Add Font</h4>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>The fonts are .ttf files that will give the style to the text on the game. You can download free fonts from <a href="https://fonts.google.com/">Google Fonts</a> or other font pages like <a href="https://www.fontsquirrel.com/">Font Squirrel</a>.</p>
        <fieldset>
          <legend>Font file (.ttf):</legend>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="input-group mb-3">
              <div class="custom-file">
                <input type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="font-input">
                <label class="custom-file-label" for="font-input">Choose file</label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <legend>Font Name</legend>
          <small class="form-text text-muted">The name will be used as key to refer to this font inside the game.</small>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input class="form-control reset-input" id="font-name" oninput="checkUniqueName(this,'fonts')">
          </div>
        </fieldset>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary upload-asset" data-dismiss="modal" onclick="uploadFont()">Add</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

